<p>The <code>exit</code> tag stops page execution.</p>

<h2>Syntax</h2>
<pre>{open}exit{close}</pre>

<h2>Exit with Message</h2>
<pre>{open}exit 'Goodbye'{close}</pre>

<h2>Conditional Exit</h2>
<pre>{open}if $unauthorized{close}
  &lt;p&gt;Access denied&lt;/p&gt;
  {open}exit{close}
{open}/if{close}</pre>

<h2>Early Exit Pattern</h2>
<pre>{open}if $done{close}
  {open}exit{close}
{open}/if{close}
{open}!-- This code only runs if not done --{close}</pre>

<h2>Note</h2>
<p>Exit immediately stops all template processing.</p>
<p><i>Not demonstrated to avoid stopping page execution.</i></p>
